Two drug addicts are cooking a small fry in the kitchen. One asks:
- Kolyas, what do you think will happen if one drinks all this in one fell swoop?
Strollers:
- Yes, you're bleeding in one gulp from your ears, from your eyes, from your nose, from your mouth.
The one to him:
- I wonder why else?
Kolyas:
- But because I'm going to smash everything with this ladle!
